<img alt="Night markets pattaya 3 in Pattaya, Thailand" height="428" loading="lazy" src="../Pattaya-Tum-Gorseller-Resized/night-markets-pattaya-3.webp" width="760"/>
<figcaption>Night Markets Pattaya 3 – explore Pattaya's best spots</figcaption>
</figure>

<p>The single biggest planning mistake is showing up to Thepprasit on a Tuesday — it's a weekend-only market. Here's the at-a-glance on opening nights, vibe and cost.</p>
<div class="verdict">
