<img alt="North vs south pattaya 3 in Pattaya, Thailand" height="428" loading="lazy" src="../Pattaya-Tum-Gorseller-Resized/north-vs-south-pattaya-3.webp" width="760"/>
<figcaption>North Vs South Pattaya 3 – explore Pattaya's best spots</figcaption>
</figure>

<p>The fast verdict first, by what most people actually care about, then the full table. Prices are 2026 baht for mid-range, in-season travel.</p>
<div class="verdict">
