<li><a href="#food-drink">Food, drink &amp;amp; beach clubs</a></li>
<li><a href="#water-sports">Water sports &amp;amp; things to do</a></li>
<li><a href="#getting-there">Getting between the two</a></li>
<li><a href="#where-to-stay">Where to stay near each</a></li>
