<h1>Pattaya on a <em>Budget</em>: 7 Days Under ฿15,000</h1>
<p class="sub">Real numbers, not survival mode. Where to sleep, eat, get around and what to skip for a full week in Pattaya under ฿15,000 (~$420) — every ฿ price verified on the ground, no spam, no affiliate distortion.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">DR</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Daniel Reyes</b>
<span>Travel editor · planning &amp; budgets, 5 years across Chonburi</span>
</div>
