<div class="compare-head">
<h3>Pattaya transport, cheapest to worst-value</h3>
<div class="legend">
<span class="lg"><span style="background:var(--green-500)"></span>Best value</span>
<span class="lg"><span style="background:var(--amber-500)"></span>Use sparingly</span>
</div>
</div>
