<div class="qv-detail">฿2,500–4,500/day for two adults + two kids</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="compare-wrap">
<div class="compare-head"><b>Pattaya for families — the honest scorecard</b><span>Mid-range, in-season, 2026 ฿</span></div>
<div class="cmp-scroll">
