<h1>Pattaya in <em>high season</em> vs low season: when to go?</h1>
<p class="sub">Pattaya's high season is dry, busy and pricier; its low season is cheaper, quieter and wetter. We compare the two on weather, crowds, price and what's open — with real 2026 baht prices and an honest verdict by traveller type.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">DR</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Daniel Reyes</b>
<span>Travel editor · 5 years across Chonburi</span>
</div>
