<span class="priceband">Skip</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="rest-body">
<div class="best-for">Choppy water · injury risk</div>
<h3>Jet ski &amp; parasailing</h3>
<div class="rest-stat">
<span class="s"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16 is-muted"><use href="#pg-pin"></use></svg> Pattaya / Jomtien beach</span>
<span class="dot"></span><span>Operators often refuse to launch</span>
</div>
<p>Choppy monsoon water makes jet skis genuinely dangerous, and parasailing is both wind-dependent and visually dull under grey skies. Pattaya's jet ski scams (inflated "damage" claims) are well documented even in good weather — add bad conditions and it's an easy no. If you want to be on the water, swap to a sheltered <a class="inline" href="blog-best-beaches-pattaya.html">beach morning</a> instead.</p>
