<!-- HOTEL DEALS -->
<h2 id="hotel-deals">The hotel discount reality</h2>
<p>This is the part travel articles consistently undersell. The real-money gap between dry-season and wet-season Pattaya isn't a polite 10% — it's <strong>30 to 50 percent off</strong> identical rooms, sometimes more. Here are rates our editors tracked from January (peak) to August (wet) at the same properties.</p>
