s run year-round. Visibility drops from about 12 m in dry season to roughly 6–8 m in the wet, and surface conditions can be choppy. Wreck dives off Koh Sak hold up well because the wrecks are sheltered. Avoid open-sea dives during active storms; reputable shops cancel automatically and refund."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "What's the best weather app for Pattaya?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Windy.com (the app or website) is the most accurate for short-term storm tracking — locals use it. AccuWeather is good for hourly forecasts. The Thai Meteorological Department app (TMD) is the official source. Avoid generic 7-day forecasts during monsoon; they're often wrong, so check the same morning instead."}}]}]$b$);
