<h1>Is <em>Pattaya</em> Safe? An Honest 2026 Safety Guide</h1>
<p class="sub">Petty crime, scams, scooter risks and solo travel — what to actually watch for in Pattaya, written by editors who live here, with real ฿ prices and the numbers to save before you fly.</p>
<div class="author-strip">
<div class="av">OV</div>
<div class="who">
<b>Olga Vavilova</b>
<span>Senior writer · 7 years in Pattaya · areas &amp; safety</span>
</div>
<div class="as-meta">
<span class="when">
<svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16 is-muted"><use href="#pg-clock"></use></svg>
            Updated Jun 7, 2026
          </span>
<div class="share-btns">
<button aria-label="Share this article" type="button"><svg aria-hidden="true" class="pg-icon is-16"><use href="#pg-share"></use></svg></button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
